{"tid":1217820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家小心，尋晚有私家車捉人","createTime":"2019-06-13T14:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T14:54:04.000Z","uid":241310,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7347602a2e2b996d21da68e469ed20556d43935c","tid":1217820,"uid":241310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:08:18.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">[13Jun / 20:08]\n\n已証實為現場消息來源，亦有組織在跟進事件：\n\n//尋晚凌晨（13Jun）我見到有細路被捉上私家車\n唔係警車，係私家車！\n-----\n有物資站細路被拉，話佢「藏有工具可作非法用途」\n物資無左可以再買，人就拉一個少一個\n香港叫人課金再買易過叫人出條命\n\n我真係屌班大人，而加處理物資嘅好多都係細路，畀警蟲嚇一嚇認咗就仆街\n你班大人去撚咗邊道？？？\n有咩唔對路都請你拉埋身邊嘅人走\n急救用品、水同眼罩都還好，頭盔就比較高危\n\n所以請放棄物資，尤其保護細路//</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1492930817622505/photos/a.1493033070945613/2352558658326379/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1492930817622505%2Fphotos%2Fa.1493033070945613%2F2352558658326379%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjexpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=4777bce7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1492930817622505/photos/a.1493033070945613/2352558658326379/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\nSource：<code>\n\n呢幾年幫咗好多義士手嘅組織，可信的，係admin現實中認識嘅人，唔係路邊社。\n</code>"},{"pid":"e1f9c189f32b699c9391e1b38394012076dc0e54","tid":1217820,"uid":54415,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:10:02.000Z","msg":"係邊區俾人拉"},{"pid":"8dea7bf37dd6c25161653f7ca76ad571d64eaa7a","tid":1217820,"uid":241310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c8bee8e69c2053bc043392a9d3fbf1a8803dae","tid":1217820,"uid":241310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1f9c189f32b699c9391e1b38394012076dc0e54","tid":1217820,"uid":54415,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:10:02.000Z","msg":"係邊區俾人拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:13:14.000Z","msg":"個組織而加忙到仆街，暫時未知<br 